Class BAParsers

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.automatalib.serialization.ba.BAParsers
  • public final class BAParsers

    Facade for BA parsing. For further information about the BA format, see https://languageinclusion.org/doku.php?id=tools#the_ba_format.
